claim.claim-text:
1. A label issuing device comprising:
an imaging portion;
an image output portion that outputs an image captured by the imaging portion;
an object recognition portion that recognizes a specific object by reading a feature amount of the output images;
an information reading portion that reads information related to the recognized object from a file storing the information related to the recognized object;
a label issuing portion that prints the read information related to the object on a label and issues the label;
a normal/defective product determination portion that compares a similarity between the output image and a predetermined reference image with a predetermined threshold to determine that the object is not a normal product when the similarity does not exceed the threshold; and
a defective product notification portion that sends a notification indicating that the object is not a normal product when the normal/defective product determination portion determines that the object is not a normal product.

9. A label issuing method comprising:
outputting an image captured by an imaging portion;
recognizing a specific object by reading a feature amount of the output images;
reading information related to the recognized object from a file storing the information related to the recognized object;
printing the read information related to the object on a label and issuing the label;
comparing a similarity between the output image and a predetermined reference image with a predetermined threshold to determine that the object is not a normal product when the similarity does not exceed the threshold; and
sending a notification indicating that the object is not a normal product when the object is determined not to be a normal product.
